Spasstik continues to pounhe ground furriously, trying to increase his
speed, then quickly coils down as the train gains ahead of him. Then his
powerful legs spring forward launghing him into the compartment. He
gently walks up to the console and places the welker rifle on the dash,
then begins to pace nervously, until he turns three times. He then
collapses into a lying down position, and snarls quietly.
